# Unbound DNS 服务器设置指南

## 什么是 Unbound？

Unbound 是一个递归 DNS 解析器，支持 DNSSEC 验证、缓存、本地 DNS 服务。

## 安装 Unbound
```bash
# openSUSE
sudo zypper install unbound

# 检查版本
unbound -V

# 启动服务
sudo systemctl start unbound
sudo systemctl enable unbound

# 查看状态
sudo systemctl status unbound
```

## 配置文件位置
```bash
# 主配置文件
/etc/unbound/unbound.conf

# 或使用 include 模式
/etc/unbound/unbound.conf.d/
```

## 基本配置

### 备份原配置
```bash
sudo cp /etc/unbound/unbound.conf /etc/unbound/unbound.conf.backup
```

### 编辑配置
```bash
sudo nano /etc/unbound/unbound.conf
```

### 基本配置示例
```yaml
server:
    # 监听接口
    interface: 127.0.0.1
    interface: ::1
    
    # 如果要让局域网访问
    # interface: 0.0.0.0
    # interface: ::0
    
    # 监听端口
    port: 53
    
    # 访问控制
    access-control: 127.0.0.0/8 allow
    access-control: ::1 allow
    
    # 局域网访问（如果需要）
    # access-control: 192.168.1.0/24 allow
    
    # 拒绝其他所有
    access-control: 0.0.0.0/0 refuse
    
    # 隐藏身份和版本
    hide-identity: yes
    hide-version: yes
    
    # DNSSEC
    auto-trust-anchor-file: "/var/lib/unbound/root.key"
    
    # 性能优化
    num-threads: 4
    msg-cache-slabs: 8
    rrset-cache-slabs: 8
    infra-cache-slabs: 8
    key-cache-slabs: 8
    
    # 缓存大小
    rrset-cache-size: 256m
    msg-cache-size: 128m
    
    # 其他缓存设置
    cache-min-ttl: 3600
    cache-max-ttl: 86400
    
    # 预取（提高性能）
    prefetch: yes
    prefetch-key: yes
    
    # 日志
    verbosity: 1
    logfile: "/var/log/unbound/unbound.log"
    log-queries: no
    log-replies: no
    
    # 隐私保护
    qname-minimisation: yes
    
    # 允许的最大并发查询
    outgoing-range: 8192
    
    # TCP 支持
    do-tcp: yes
    
    # IPv4/IPv6
    do-ip4: yes
    do-ip6: no
    
    # Root hints (根服务器)
    root-hints: "/var/lib/unbound/root.hints"
    
    # 私有地址反向解析
    private-address: 10.0.0.0/8
    private-address: 172.16.0.0/12
    private-address: 192.168.0.0/16
    private-address: 169.254.0.0/16
    private-address: fd00::/8
    private-address: fe80::/10
```

## 下载 Root Hints
```bash
# 创建目录
sudo mkdir -p /var/lib/unbound

# 下载 root hints
sudo wget https://www.internic.net/domain/named.root -O /var/lib/unbound/root.hints

# 设置权限
sudo chown unbound:unbound /var/lib/unbound/root.hints
```

## 设置 DNSSEC
```bash
# 生成 root key
sudo unbound-anchor -a /var/lib/unbound/root.key

# 或者
sudo unbound-control-setup

# 设置权限
sudo chown unbound:unbound /var/lib/unbound/root.key
```

## 创建日志目录
```bash
sudo mkdir -p /var/log/unbound
sudo chown unbound:unbound /var/log/unbound
sudo touch /var/log/unbound/unbound.log
sudo chown unbound:unbound /var/log/unbound/unbound.log
```

## 本地 DNS 记录

### 创建本地域名解析
```bash
sudo nano /etc/unbound/unbound.conf.d/local-zone.conf
```

添加：
```yaml
server:
    # 本地域名
    local-zone: "home.lan." static
    
    # 本地主机记录
    local-data: "router.home.lan. IN A 192.168.1.1"
    local-data: "server.home.lan. IN A 192.168.1.100"
    local-data: "nas.home.lan. IN A 192.168.1.50"
    
    # 反向解析
    local-data-ptr: "192.168.1.1 router.home.lan"
    local-data-ptr: "192.168.1.100 server.home.lan"
```

## 广告过滤

### 方法1：使用 Unbound 内置过滤
```bash
sudo nano /etc/unbound/unbound.conf.d/adblock.conf
```

添加：
```yaml
server:
    # 阻止广告域名
    local-zone: "doubleclick.net" refuse
    local-zone: "googlesyndication.com" refuse
    local-zone: "googleadservices.com" refuse
    local-zone: "google-analytics.com" refuse
```

### 方法2：使用黑名单文件
```bash
# 下载广告域名列表
sudo wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/StevenBlack/hosts/master/hosts -O /tmp/adblock.hosts

# 转换为 Unbound 格式
sudo awk '/^0.0.0.0/ {print "local-zone: \""$2"\" refuse"}' /tmp/adblock.hosts > /etc/unbound/unbound.conf.d/adblock.conf

# 重启 Unbound
sudo systemctl restart unbound
```

## 转发到上游 DNS

### 转发到 Cloudflare
```bash
sudo nano /etc/unbound/unbound.conf.d/forward.conf
```

添加：
```yaml
forward-zone:
    name: "."
    # Cloudflare
    forward-addr: 1.1.1.1@853#cloudflare-dns.com
    forward-addr: 1.0.0.1@853#cloudflare-dns.com
    forward-ssl-upstream: yes
```

### 转发到 Google
```yaml
forward-zone:
    name: "."
    forward-addr: 8.8.8.8@853
    forward-addr: 8.8.4.4@853
    forward-ssl-upstream: yes
```

### 转发到 Quad9
```yaml
forward-zone:
    name: "."
    forward-addr: 9.9.9.9@853
    forward-addr: 149.112.112.112@853
    forward-ssl-upstream: yes
```

### 转发到 DNSCrypt-Proxy
```yaml
forward-zone:
    name: "."
    forward-addr: 127.0.0.1@5353
```

## 启动和管理
```bash
# 测试配置文件
sudo unbound-checkconf

# 启动
sudo systemctl start unbound

# 重启
sudo systemctl restart unbound

# 停止
sudo systemctl stop unbound

# 开机自启
sudo systemctl enable unbound

# 查看状态
sudo systemctl status unbound

# 查看日志
sudo tail -f /var/log/unbound/unbound.log
# 或
sudo journalctl -u unbound -f
```

## 配置系统使用 Unbound
```bash
# 方法1：修改 resolv.conf
echo "nameserver 127.0.0.1" | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf

# 方法2：NetworkManager
sudo nmcli connection modify "连接名" ipv4.dns "127.0.0.1"
sudo nmcli connection modify "连接名" ipv4.ignore-auto-dns yes
sudo nmcli connection down "连接名"
sudo nmcli connection up "连接名"
```

## 测试 Unbound
```bash
# 基本测试
dig @127.0.0.1 google.com

# 测试 DNSSEC
dig @127.0.0.1 +dnssec google.com

# 测试本地域名
dig @127.0.0.1 router.home.lan

# 查看缓存统计
sudo unbound-control stats_noreset

# 清除缓存
sudo unbound-control flush_zone .
sudo unbound-control reload
```

## Unbound 控制命令
```bash
# 查看统计信息
sudo unbound-control stats

# 重新加载配置
sudo unbound-control reload

# 清除缓存
sudo unbound-control flush_zone example.com

# 清除所有缓存
sudo unbound-control flush_zone .

# 转储缓存
sudo unbound-control dump_cache

# 查看状态
sudo unbound-control status

# 查看配置
sudo unbound-control get_option

# 列出本地zone
sudo unbound-control list_local_zones

# 列出本地数据
sudo unbound-control list_local_data
```

## 性能优化
```yaml
server:
    # 增加线程数
    num-threads: 4
    
    # 增加缓存
    rrset-cache-size: 512m
    msg-cache-size: 256m
    
    # 预取
    prefetch: yes
    prefetch-key: yes
    
    # 增加并发数
    outgoing-range: 8192
    num-queries-per-thread: 4096
    
    # SO_REUSEPORT
    so-reuseport: yes
    
    # 减少超时
    infra-host-ttl: 900
```

